@startuml
[*] --> WaitingForSale : wait for new sale
WaitingForSale --> AddingItems : enter items one by one
AddingItems --> Payment : move to payment after all items have been added
Payment --> VerifyingPayment : verify payment if customer pays by card or check
VerifyingPayment --> ApprovedPayment : complete sale once payment is approved
ApprovedPayment --> SaleCompleted : return to waiting for next customer
SaleCompleted --> WaitingForSale : wait for new sale

WaitingForSale --> Payment : complete sale immediately if customer pays with cash
@enduml
